{"tha-ap162:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap162:0.2":"Bandhujivakavagga ","tha-ap162:0.3":"Kumudadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap162:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap162:1.2":"mahajatassaro ahu; ","tha-ap162:1.3":"Padumuppalasanchanno, ","tha-ap162:1.4":"pundarikasamotthato. ","tha-ap162:2.1":"Kukuttho nama namena, ","tha-ap162:2.2":"tatthasim sakuno tada; ","tha-ap162:2.3":"Silava buddhisampanno, ","tha-ap162:2.4":"punnapunnesu kovido. ","tha-ap162:3.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap162:3.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap162:3.3":"Jatassarassavidure, ","tha-ap162:3.4":"sancarittha mahamuni. ","tha-ap162:4.1":"Jalajam kumudam chetva, ","tha-ap162:4.2":"upanesim mahesino; ","tha-ap162:4.3":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap162:4.4":"patiggahi mahamuni. ","tha-ap162:5.1":"Tanca danam daditvana, ","tha-ap162:5.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap162:5.3":"Kappanam satasahassam, ","tha-ap162:5.4":"duggatim nupapajjaham. ","tha-ap162:6.1":"Solaseto kappasate, ","tha-ap162:6.2":"asum varunanamaka; ","tha-ap162:6.3":"Attha ete janadhipa, ","tha-ap162:6.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap162:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap162:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap162:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap162:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kumudadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap162:9.1":"Kumudadayakattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap162:10.1":"Bandhujivakavaggo solasamo. ","tha-ap162:11.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap162:12.1":"Bandhujivo tambapupphi, ","tha-ap162:12.2":"vithikakkarupupphiyo; ","tha-ap162:12.3":"Mandaravo kadambi ca, ","tha-ap162:12.4":"sulako nagapupphiyo; ","tha-ap162:12.5":"Punnago komudi gatha, ","tha-ap162:12.6":"chappannasa pakittitati. "}